<p>The processing of data necessary for the fulfilment of such obligations is required to ensure a correct browsing of the website and the provision of such data is mandatory in order to implement the aforementioned purposes. Failure to acquire such data may result in the inability to guarantee the correct navigation of the website.</p>
<p>&#8211; Third party advertising cookies (no user profiling is carried out)</p>
